===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Morty (Masters)}}
Morty forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Drifblim}}, {{p|Mismagius}}, {{p|Banette}}, {{Shiny}} {{p|Ho-Oh}}, {{p|Gastly}}, and {{rf|Hisuian}} {{p|Typhlosion}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. His Banette is capable of [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolving]]. Morty became a playable sync pair on July 15, 2020.

Morty has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]].

